IZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用突擊個廢盾檔住對面主天使號個陽電子破壞砲<br />\n仲要唔死 最後去左渣天意高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n渣天意？你肯定？"},{"pid":"7a49cedf26774466d402aebd181a09fcd2f17d41","tid":34733,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQcRr3H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQcRr3H.jpg&h=74b5f0e9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用突擊個廢盾檔住對面主天使號個陽電子破壞砲<br />\n仲要唔死 最後去左渣天意高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n渣天意？你肯定？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然seed d好撚垃圾 不過你都係重睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e8b11778b760dcfecbdc2bbdd77d284b0215b8","tid":34733,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:41:05.000Z","msg":"渡久地東亞<br />\n<br />\n意志力no.1，面對極大壓力可以眼都唔眨<br />\n<br />\n最強賭徒，無論係智力上定賭品上。因為輸比兒島，所以應承佢帶領球隊拎冠軍，結果真係做到，願賭服輸最高境界。<br />\n<br />\n唔信任任何人人，只會利用，但係出乎意料地重視信任呢樣野。係佢既最後一場比賽，所有隊友都信任佢（個場比賽佢比人屈機，如果輸左全隊冇糧出，但係隊友繼續比佢投球），結果佢成功拎左陪葬品"},{"pid":"0cf3162bfac749fdf999ddf1da681c9e0fb2b2f7","tid":34733,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:47:52.000Z","msg":"其實仲有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n帶土都係<br />\n<br />\n佢卡卡西琳個故事好睇過鳴人佐助港女櫻好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實都唔算係一廂情願，起碼係死個刻琳有黎接佢，唔會眼尾都望"},{"pid":"31fb424c5ab909cdc83b562f2f46911ad9e1b433","tid":34733,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實仲有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n帶土都係<br />\n<br />\n佢卡卡西琳個故事好睇過鳴人佐助港女櫻好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實都唔算係一廂情願，起碼係死個刻琳有黎接佢，唔會眼尾都唔望</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d07a9262daad4e4f5738372951fa18c65e1cef0b","tid":34733,"uid":45228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"巴達克--龍珠<br />\n為咗幫自己嘅同伴報仇<br />\n唔理自己有幾重傷，面對幾多敵人，實力差幾遠，都直接衝入去敵人群中，為嘅唔係自己，而係自己嘅同伴被菲利出賣。<br />\n無一刻嘅恐懼同猶疑，真係超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面巴打講火影個啲人物都超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}